<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>iOS Device UDID Grabber</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f5f5f7;
        }

        .container {
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 2rem;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #1d1d1f;
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .description {
            color: #515154;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .steps {
            margin: 2rem 0;
        }

        .step {
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            padding-left: 2rem;
            position: relative;
        }

        .step:before {
            content: counter(step-counter);
            counter-increment: step-counter;
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
            background-color: #0071e3;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .download-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #0071e3;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            margin-top: 1rem;
            transition: background-color 0.2s;
        }

        .download-btn:hover {
            background-color: #0077ed;
        }

        .note {
            margin-top: 2rem;
            padding: 1rem;
            background-color: #f5f5f7;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #515154;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>iOS Device UDID Grabber</h1>
        <p class="description">Get your iOS device's UDID in just a few simple steps</p>
        
        <div class="steps">
            <div class="step">
                <h3>Download Profile</h3>
                <p>Click the button below to download the configuration profile.</p>
                <a href="/profile" class="download-btn">Download Profile</a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="step">
                <h3>Install Profile</h3>
                <p>Open the downloaded profile and install it on your iOS device. You'll need to go to Settings and approve the profile installation.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="step">
                <h3>View Results</h3>
                <p>After installation, your device information will be displayed on the next page.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="note">
            <strong>Note:</strong> This process is completely secure and only collects basic device information needed for development purposes. No personal data is collected or stored.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 